    <title>配置Sublime Text 3文本编辑器</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2019/03/13/%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AESublime-Text-3%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2019/03/13/配置Sublime-Text-3文本编辑器/</id>
    <published>2019-03-13T15:13:24.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-03-14T06:10:26.770Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="配置”Sublime-Text-3”文本编辑器"><a href="#配置”Sublime-Text-3”文本编辑器" class="headerlink" title="配置”Sublime Text 3”文本编辑器"></a>配置”Sublime Text 3”文本编辑器</h1><h2 id="目录"><a href="#目录" class="headerlink" title="目录"></a>目录</h2><p>​    一. 下载</p><p>​    二. 破解</p><p>​    三. 更改语言（将默认的”英文”界面改成”中文”界面，语言不止这里两种哟）</p><p>​    四. 安装所需的插件</p><h2 id="一-下载"><a href="#一-下载" class="headerlink" title="一. 下载"></a>一. 下载</h2><p>​    官网链接：<a href="https://www.sublimetext.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">sublimetext</a></p><p>​    蓝奏云：<a href="https://www.lanzous.com/i3eqs5g" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sublime Text Build 3176 x64 Setup.exe</a></p><p>​    所下版本：<strong>(Version 3.1.1,Build 3176)</strong></p><p>​    <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dawzxdbxn/image/upload/v1552543550/%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AESublimeText%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8/OAO_2019-03-12_23-34-31.png" alt="官网界面，点击 &quot;DOWNLOAD FOR WINDOWS&quot;下载"></p><h2 id="二-破解-给予授权，注册"><a href="#二-破解-给予授权，注册" class="headerlink" title="二. 破解,(给予授权，注册)"></a>二. 破解,(给予授权，注册)</h2><p><strong>3.1 3176 可用注册码</strong></p><p>此验证码为sublime text3 注册码，非sublime text2 注册码。</p><p>加入到<code>hosts</code>文件</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">127.0.0.1       www.sublimetext.com</span><br><span class="line">127.0.0.1       license.sublimehq.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Windows : <code>c:/windows/system32/drivers/etc/hosts</code></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">----- BEGIN LICENSE -----</span><br><span class="line">sgbteam</span><br><span class="line">Single User License</span><br><span class="line">EA7E-1153259</span><br><span class="line">8891CBB9 F1513E4F 1A3405C1 A865D53F</span><br><span class="line">115F202E 7B91AB2D 0D2A40ED 352B269B</span><br><span class="line">76E84F0B CD69BFC7 59F2DFEF E267328F</span><br><span class="line">215652A3 E88F9D8F 4C38E3BA 5B2DAAE4</span><br><span class="line">969624E7 DC9CD4D5 717FB40C 1B9738CF</span><br><span class="line">20B3C4F1 E917B5B3 87C38D9C ACCE7DD8</span><br><span class="line">5F7EF854 86B9743C FADC04AA FB0DA5C0</span><br><span class="line">F913BE58 42FEA319 F954EFDD AE881E0B</span><br><span class="line">------ END LICENSE ------</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="三-更改语言-英-》中"><a href="#三-更改语言-英-》中" class="headerlink" title="三. 更改语言(英 ==》中)"></a>三. 更改语言(英 ==》中)</h2><p>在sublime里点击  <code>Tools --&gt;install package control(进行安装package control)</code></p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dawzxdbxn/image/upload/v1552543550/%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AESublimeText%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8/OAO_2019-03-13_00-00-11.png" alt="install package control"></p><p>Preferences（快捷键 ctrl+shift+p）–》package control –》install package</p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dawzxdbxn/image/upload/v1552543550/%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AESublimeText%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8/OAO_2019-03-13_00-03-46.png" alt="install package"></p><p>接着输入  ChineseLocalizations 安装</p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dawzxdbxn/image/upload/v1552543550/%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AESublimeText%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8/OAO_2019-03-13_00-04-55.png" alt="install ChineseLocalizations"></p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dawzxdbxn/image/upload/v1552543550/%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AESublimeText%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8/OAO_2019-03-13_00-06-04.png" alt="view"></p><h2 id="四-安装所需插件"><a href="#四-安装所需插件" class="headerlink" title="四. 安装所需插件"></a>四. 安装所需插件</h2><p>Sublime Text3是一款给力的文本编辑器，通过安装插件可以编辑Markdown文本，在编辑Markdown文本的同时可以实时预览编辑效果。</p><hr><p>安装准备：</p><ul><li>找到菜单栏：<code>Preferences</code> → <code>Package Control</code> → <code>Package Control:Install Package</code>；</li><li>没有找到<code>Package Control</code>，那么点击<a href="https://packagecontrol.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Package Control</a> 安装吧，安装完重启Sublime。</li></ul><p>安装过程：</p><ul><li>需要两款插件：<code>Markdown Editing + OmniMarkupPreviewer</code>；</li><li>在<code>Package Control</code> → <code>Install Package</code>中输入两款插件的名字，找到相应插件，点击即可自动完成安装，安装完重启Sublime；</li><li>简单设置：<code>Preferences</code> → <code>Package Settings</code> → <code>OmniMarkupPreviewer</code> →<code>Setting——User</code>，</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;renderer_options-MarkdownRenderer&quot;:</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;extensions&quot;: [&quot;tables&quot;, &quot;fenced_code&quot;, &quot;codehilite&quot;],</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;parser&quot;: &quot;markdown&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;enabled_parsers&quot;: [&quot;markdown&quot;]</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>支持 <code>latex</code>语法：<code>Preferences</code> → <code>Package Settings</code> → <code>OmniMarkupPreviewer</code> → <code>Setting——Default</code>，</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&quot;mathjax_enabled&quot;: true,// 支持 latex语法</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更改主题颜色：</p><p>Markdown默认主题颜色为白色的，不美观。把<code>Preferences</code>→ <code>Package Settings</code> → <code>Markdown Editing</code> → <code>Markdown GFM Setting——Default</code>复制到<code>Preferences</code> → <code>Package Settings</code> → <code>Markdown Editing</code> → <code>Markdown GFM Setting——User</code>中，更改代码：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// &quot;color_scheme&quot;: &quot;Packages/MarkdownEditing/MarkdownEditor.tmTheme&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">&quot;color_scheme&quot;: &quot;Packages/MarkdownEditing/MarkdownEditor-Dark.tmTheme&quot;,</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用方法： 使用Sublime新建一个文件，右下角选择编辑方式为“Markdown”，将其保存为.md文件，选择保存位置并单击确定，输入快捷键：<code>Ctrl+Alt+O</code>，打开浏览器界面预览即可。</p>]]></content>
    
